name: SayeBrook
address: 1135 Milford Way, Myrtle Beach, South Carolina 29588
description:
ABOUT THE HOME ENERGY RATING SCALE
The HERS (Home Energy Rating System) Index allows buyers to compare the relative energy efficiency of different homes. The HERS Index home energy rating is determined by an independent RESNET-certified home energy rater ("Rater"). The lower a home’s score, the more energy efficient it is in comparison to the HERS referenced home. For every one-point decrease in the HERS Index score, there is a corresponding one percent (1%) reduction in energy consumption as compared to a home with a HERS Index of 100. A home with a HERS score of 100 reflects a home built to 2006 IEEC Building Codes. See the bottom of this page for more information on HERS scores.

amenities.name: Amenities include
amenities.description: Amenities include a community clubhouse, a resort-style pool with swim lanes, a pool pavilion, children's playground, fire pit, pickleball, bocce and basketball courts, and a great lawn with a movie screen!

amenities.name: Only miles
amenities.description: Only 2 miles to shopping, dining and entertainment in The Market Common

amenities.name: Spend afternoon
amenities.description: Spend the afternoon at Surfside Beach, just 3 miles away

amenities.name: Central location
amenities.description: Central location between the heart of Myrtle Beach and Conway

amenities.name: Easy access
amenities.description: Easy access right off of Hwy-544 for easy connectivity to US-17 and US-501

amenities.name: Less than
amenities.description: Less than 9 miles to Broadway at the Beach

amenities.name: Less than
amenities.description: Less than 6 miles to Coastal Grand Mall and 8 miles to Waccamaw Mall

amenities.name: Dozens golf
amenities.description: Dozens of golf courses within 10 miles of this new home community

amenities.name: Square Footage
amenities.description: Walk to major retails at SayeBrook Town Square, including Target, Marshalls, Kirkland's, Ulta and more.

amenities.name: Home Designs
amenities.description: Shop at Kohl's or Lowe's Home Improvement just across the street

amenities.name: Bathrooms
amenities.description: Shop the 30 boutiques and major retailers, including Pottery Barn, White House Black Market, Southern Living, Anthropologie, Bath & Body Works, Orvis, Chicos, J. Jill, and more at the Market Common

amenities.name: Grab quick
amenities.description: Grab a quick bite to eat at one of the many restaurants nearby including Which Wich Sandwiches, Moe's Southwest Grill, Panera Bread, McDonald's, Zaxby's, California Dreaming, Chipotle, McAlister's Deli, Mod Pizza, BurgerFi, Lucky Panda, and more.

amenities.name: Dine one
amenities.description: Dine in at one of the many popular restaurants in The Market Common including Tupelo Honey, King Street Grille, Gordon Biersch Brewery, Nacho Hippo, CO Sushi, P.F. Chang's, Ultimate California Pizza, Travinia Italian Kitchen, Crepe Creation Café, or Cold Stone Creamery.

amenities.name: walking distance
amenities.description: In walking distance to South Strand Medical Center Hospital

amenities.name: Only miles
amenities.description: Only 10 miles from Coastal Carolina University
